OL,4,G1100FFantastic Voyage
OL,5,     GThis film's sci-fi, not auteur.
OL,6,     GPint-sized medics become
OL,7,     Gvoyageurs. Add oceanological; to
OL,8,     Ghaematological. Not to mention a
OL,9,     Ghidd'n saboteur. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,10,G1305FThe Incredible Shrinking Man
OL,11,     GScott's getting smaller; a
OL,12,     Gnuclear thing. The cat getting
OL,13,     Gbolder, scaring him. Lives in a
OL,14,     Gdollhouse. Longs for a friend.
OL,15,     GQuestions his sanity. Will his
OL,16,     Gshrinking end? _WorldPoetryDay
