OL,4,G1455FRat Race
OL,5,     GScrewball farce with a well-known
OL,6,     Gcast. There's $2m at stake to be
OL,7,     Gfirst across the States, while
OL,8,     GJohn Cleese bets on all the
OL,9,     Gchases. It's all a bit like Wacky
OL,10,     GRaces. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G1705FMade in Italy
OL,12,     GDrama set in Italy. A widower and
OL,13,     Ga divorcee. Father's Robert,
OL,14,     GJack's his son. Both estranged
OL,15,     Gsince Jack was young. Bonding on
OL,16,     Ga renovation: Tuscan
OL,17,     Greconciliation. _WorldPoetryDay
