OL,16,G2100FCaptain Phillips
OL,17,     GTom Hanks gazes anxiously, from
OL,18,     Gthe vessel's bow. Barkhad Abdi's
OL,19,     Gpirates board; he's the captain
OL,20,     Gnow. _WorldPoetryDay
